snippet.title: Bayonetta 2 Short Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Bayonetta comes to Nintendo Switch! Purchase the packaged version of Bayonetta 2 and receive a download code for Bayonetta, as well.

Bayonetta 2 is available 2/16! https://goo.gl/1nHmwR

#NintendoSwitch #Bayonetta2

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com
